flowchart TD

    A[Admin opens Email Notification menu] --> B{Choose Notification Type}

    B --> C[Module Completion]
    B --> D[Assignments Review]
    B --> E[Assignments Approved]
    B --> F[Assignments Rejected]
    B --> G[Certificate Created]
    B --> H[Signup]

    %% Common configuration flow
    C --> I[Load template configuration]
    D --> I
    E --> I
    F --> I
    G --> I
    H --> I

    I --> J[Admin edits enable status recipients subject body]
    J --> K[Click Save Changes]
    K --> L[Store template settings]

    L --> M{Admin clicks Send Test?}
    M -->|Yes| N[Input Send To email]
    N --> O[Render template with sample data]
    O --> P[Send test email]
    P --> Q[Store email log]
    M -->|No| R[Wait for automated trigger]

    %% Module Completion automated flow
    R --> S{Student completes all lessons in a module?}
    S -->|Yes| T[Load Module Completion template]
    T --> U[Render module completion placeholders]
    U --> V[Send to admin and user]
    V --> W[Store email log]

    %% Assignment Review automated flow
    R --> X{Student submits assignment?}
    X -->|Yes| Y[Load Assignments Review template]
    Y --> Z[Render assignment review placeholders]
    Z --> AA[Send review notification]
    AA --> AB[Store email log]

    %% Assignment Approved automated flow
    R --> AC{Admin approves assignment?}
    AC -->|Yes| AD[Load Assignments Approved template]
    AD --> AE[Render assignment approved placeholders]
    AE --> AF[Send approved notification]
    AF --> AG[Store email log]

    %% Assignment Rejected automated flow
    R --> AH{Admin rejects assignment?}
    AH -->|Yes| AI[Load Assignments Rejected template]
    AI --> AJ[Render assignment rejected placeholders plus feedback]
    AJ --> AK[Send rejected notification]
    AK --> AL[Store email log]

    %% Certificate Created automated flow
    R --> AM{Admin generates certificate or sends graduation email?}
    AM -->|Yes| AN[Load Certificate Created template]
    AN --> AO[Render certificate placeholders]
    AO --> AP[Attach PDF certificate if implemented]
    AP --> AQ[Send certificate email]
    AQ --> AR[Store email log]

    %% Signup automated flow
    R --> AS{User completes signup?}
    AS -->|Yes| AT[Load Signup template]
    AT --> AU[Render signup placeholders]
    AU --> AV[Send signup email]
    AV --> AW[Store email log]